                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17770910-87-victim677 t17770910-87-viclabel424"></join>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17770910-87-victim679 t17770910-87-viclabel424"></join>; the prisoner was our <rs id="t17770910-87-deflabel425" type="occupation">porter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17770910-87-defend675 t17770910-87-deflabel425"></join>; he left our house, and the very next day a person brought these two defaced spoons to me (producing them); they are our property; though it is attempted to be defaced here are the words Corn hill upon it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17770910-87-person682">
                  WILLIAM
                   DELFER
               <interp inst="t17770910-87-person682" type="surname" value="DELFER"></interp>
