                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>The prisoner offered these spoons to pawn; I searched him and found a spoon in his waistcoat pocket.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17770910-87-person683">
                  JOHN
                   FENTON
               <interp inst="t17770910-87-person683" type="surname" value="FENTON"></interp>
